Test 2: Esoteric Technical Specification
Task Statement
"Find the exact technical specifications for the USB-C connector's power delivery protocol version 3.1, including: maximum power wattage, voltage ranges supported, and the specific revision number of the PD specification document. Also find one real-world product that implements this exact specification and cite where the manufacturer confirms this. Provide direct links to the official specification document and the product page."

Required Deliverables
- Maximum power wattage for USB-C PD 3.1
- Voltage ranges supported
- Exact PD specification revision number
- One real product implementing PD 3.1
- Manufacturer confirmation of PD 3.1 implementation
- Link to official specification document
- Link to product page
- At least 4 distinct citations

Success Criteria
- At least 6 search actions executed
- Technical specifications are precise and accurate
- Official specification document is cited
- Real product is identified with manufacturer confirmation
- All required technical details present
- At least 4 distinct sources cited (spec doc, manufacturer, product page, technical reference)
- Information demonstrates deep technical research

